OL,3,CInquiry vows to find truth about how
OL,4,Cdeadliest Channel crossing occurred
OL,6,FThis will include considering whether
OL,7,Fsuggesting improvements "in search and
OL,8,Frescue practice ought to be made for
OL,9,Fthe benefit of all those who use these
OL,10,Fcommercially important waters between
OL,11,FFrance and the United Kingdom".
OL,13,FSir Ross, who represented Dudley North
OL,14,Fas a Labour MP between 1997 and 2005,
OL,15,Fsaid: "All of those who engage with
OL,16,Four work must do so on the clear
OL,17,Funderstanding that there is but one
OL,18,Fpurpose to the whole exercise, to find
OL,19,Fout the truth.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
