OL,3,CInquiry vows to find truth about how
OL,4,Cdeadliest Channel crossing occurred
OL,6,F"Their task is to assist the inquiry
OL,7,Fin its investigation and in getting to
OL,8,Fthe truth of what happened.
OL,10,F"To that end, I hope and expect to
OL,11,Freceive full co-operation from all of
OL,12,Fthose involved in our work.
OL,14,F"There'll be no place for obstruction
OL,15,For foot dragging on the part of those
OL,16,Fwhose involvement in the events of
OL,17,FNovember 24 2021 will be scrutinised.
OL,19,F"This is of vital importance if the
OL,20,Fwork of the inquiry is to proceed in
OL,21,Fan efficient and effective way."
