OL,4,Cdeadliest Channel crossing occurred
OL,6,Flast year found the capsized boat was
OL,7,F"wholly unsuitable and ill-equipped"
OL,8,Ffor the crossing, adding that the UK's
OL,9,Fsearch and rescue response was
OL,10,Fhampered by the lack of a dedicated
OL,11,Faircraft carrying out surveillance.
OL,13,FA pregnant woman and three children
OL,14,Fwere among the victims when a boat
OL,15,Fwhich appeared "wholly unsuited to the
OL,16,Fvoyage took on water and was swamped"
OL,17,Fbut there were "remarkably two
OL,18,Fsurvivors", Sir Ross said.
