OL,6,FDescribing Channel crossings as a
OL,7,F"politically controversial issue with
OL,8,Fsignificant humanitarian
OL,9,Fconsequences", he stressed the focus
OL,10,Fof the inquiry was not on those
OL,11,F"complex issues", had "no remit to
OL,12,Finvestigate the general problem of
OL,13,Fsmall boat crossings" and cannot
OL,14,Fbecome "a vehicle for wider debates"
OL,15,Fas he vowed: "We will not lose sight
OL,16,Fof the fact that... this was, above
OL,17,Fall, an immeasurable human tragedy."
