OL,3,CInquiry vows to find truth about how
OL,4,Cdeadliest Channel crossing occurred
OL,6,FPhillippa Kaufmann KC, who represents
OL,7,Fone of the survivors of the
OL,8,F"catastrophic" incident and the
OL,9,Ffamilies of 20 of the people who died,
OL,10,Fsaid they "wholeheartedly welcome" the
OL,11,Fopening of the inquiry, adding that it
OL,12,Fwas "something they fought hard to
OL,13,Festablish" and having "endured a long
OL,14,Fand painful wait of 27 months" were
OL,15,Fgrateful for the commitment from Sir
OL,16,FRoss to carry out a "prompt and
OL,17,Fthorough investigation".
OL,19,FShe told the hearing: "Our clients
OL,20,Fhave high hopes for this inquiry.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
