OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F418A1709827077
OL,3,CInquiry vows to find truth about how
OL,4,Cdeadliest Channel crossing occurred
OL,6,F"They hope that it is going to
OL,7,Festablish the truth as to what
OL,8,Fhappened and how it is that such a
OL,9,Fsignificant loss of life occurred. And
OL,10,Fas part of that, they hope that
OL,11,Finsofar as they were failed by any
OL,12,Fauthority tasked with planning, search
OL,13,Fand rescue operations that night in
OL,14,Fthe Channel, that those will be
OL,15,Fidentified and explained.
OL,17,F"And finally, they hope that lessons
OL,18,Fwill be learned that can help prevent
OL,19,Fsuch a terrible loss of life in the
OL,20,Ffuture."
