OL,6,FIssuing a call for evidence, the
OL,7,Finquiry, which does not have the same
OL,8,Flegal powers as a statutory probe,
OL,9,Fwill now consider the information it
OL,10,Freceives before public hearings take
OL,11,Fplace at a later date. But no
OL,12,Ftimescale has yet been set.
OL,14,FSir Ross said he would report his
OL,15,Ffindings to the Transport Secretary
OL,16,F"as soon as practicable".
